OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain at first, will
OL,7,Fgradually weaken overnight to leave a
OL,8,Frather cloudy, but mainly dry start to
OL,9,FTuesday. Fog patches across the Peak
OL,10,FDistrict. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,13,Fcloud but warm, bright spells
OL,14,Fdeveloping. However, thicker cloud and
OL,15,Frain arriving from the west through
OL,16,Fthe evening. Turning breezier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
